            <h1>Locations</h1>
            <p id="home_text">
                Brandeis University is located just nine miles from Boston and is within easy driving distance of the region's major cities. 
                Basketball, fencing, indoor track and field and volleyball are played in the <strong>Gosman Athletic Center </strong>
                while swimming and diving is held in the connected <strong>Linsey Pool</strong>. Baseball is played on <strong>Stein Diamond</strong>. Soccer is played on <strong>Gordon Field</strong>. 
                Softball is played on <strong>Marcus Field</strong>. All of these fields are visible from the parking lot in front of the Gosman Center. 
                Tennis is played on the <strong>Rieger Tennis Courts</strong>, located behind the Gosman Center.
            </p>

